title: Rin Tin Tin THE LONE DEFENDER

sources.title: Rin Tin Tin THE LONE DEFENDER
sources.description: 1930 Serial featuring Rin Tin Tin. Variable video quality from a video master. Directed by Richard Thorpe. Episode Titles: 1. The Mystery of the Desert 2. The Fugitive 3. Jaws of Peril 4. Trapped 5. Circle of Death 6. Surrounded by Law 7. The Ghost Speaks 8. The Brink of Destruction 9. The Avalanche 10.Fury of the Desert 11.Cornered 12.Vindicated!
